since he was a child.

395
00:24:23,230 --> 00:24:24,950
But recently, I realized

396
00:24:26,190 --> 00:24:27,830
that I didn't know him at all.

397
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:30,590
He liked drinking,

398
00:24:31,470 --> 00:24:32,760
