682
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:45,190
So this is just an ordinary farmhouse.

683
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,600
It's a farmhouse,

684
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:47,800
but maybe

685
00:37:48,430 --> 00:37:49,230
it's not ordinary.

686
00:37:49,390 --> 00:37:50,360
I'm afraid those people there

687
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,710
aren't ordinary farmers either.

688
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,040
What do you mean?

689
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,390
There must be something on the bodies.

690
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:58,910
The problem

691
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:01,120
