00:38:09,560 --> 00:38:12,390
Heaven help the good ones.

696
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:18,840
There are three. Just one for each of us.

697
00:38:19,870 --> 00:38:20,390
Wait.

698
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:21,280
Four.

699
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:25,230
That's weird.

